  <summary date="2024-01-05T22:35:20Z" status="Introduced in House">Stop Funding Our Adversaries Act of 2023

This bill prohibits federal agencies from conducting or supporting, either directly or indirectly, research that will be conducted by China's government, the Chinese Communist Party, or any agent, instrumentality, or entity belonging to or controlled by either entity.</summary>
